lead_paragraph: Former Heisman Trophy winner Tim Tebow recorded a pair of hits, scored a run and ended the game with a sliding grab in his final intrasquad game in the New York Mets' instructional league.

headline.print_headline: Tebow Sharp in Last Tuneup Before Instructional League Debut
